M|references|Ready-to-use templates for different platforms and cnt types.
M|references|- LinkedIn Post Templates (The Story Post, The Contrarian Take, The List Post, The How-To)
M|references|- Twitter/X Thread Templates (The Tutorial Thread, The Story Thread, The Breakdown Thread)
M|references|- Instagram Templates (The Carousel Hook, The Reel Script)
M|references|- Hook Formulas (Curiosity Hooks, Story Hooks, Value Hooks, Contrarian Hooks, soc Proof Hooks)
M|references|```
M|references|[Hook: Unexpected outcome or lesson]
M|references|[Set the scene: When/where this happened]
M|references|[The challenge you faced]
M|references|[What you tried / what happened]
M|references|[The turning point]
M|references|[The result]
M|references|[The lesson for readers]
M|references|[Question to prompt engagement]
M|references|```
M|references|```
M|references|[Unpopular opinion stated boldly]
M|references|Here's why:
M|references|[Reason 1]
M|references|[Reason 2]
M|references|[Reason 3]
M|references|[What you recommend instead]
M|references|[Invite discussion: "Am I wrong?"]
M|references|```
M|references|```
M|references|[X things I learned about [topic] after [credibility builder]:
M|references|1. [Point] — [Brief explanation]
M|references|2. [Point] — [Brief explanation]
M|references|3. [Point] — [Brief explanation]
M|references|[Wrap-up insight]
M|references|Which resonates most with you?
M|references|```
M|references|```
M|references|How to [achieve outcome] in [timeframe]:
M|references|Step 1: [Action]
M|references|↳ [Why this matters]
M|references|Step 2: [Action]
M|references|↳ [Key detail]
M|references|Step 3: [Action]
M|references|↳ [Common mistake to avoid]
M|references|[Result you can expect]
M|references|[CTA or question]
M|references|```
M|references|```
M|references|Tweet 1: [Hook + promise of value]
M|references|"Here's exactly how to [outcome] (step-by-step):"
M|references|Tweet 2-7: [One step per tweet with details]
M|references|Final tweet: [Summary + CTA]
M|references|"If this was helpful, follow me for more on [topic]"
M|references|```
M|references|```
M|references|Tweet 1: [Intriguing hook]
M|references|"[Time] ago, [unexpected thing happened]. Here's the full story:"
M|references|Tweet 2-6: [Story beats, building tension]
M|references|Tweet 7: [Resolution and lesson]
M|references|Final tweet: [Takeaway + engagement ask]
M|references|```
M|references|```
